strings:
<voice_0x010012D1><se_low>King Trode: I shouldn't have to p-put up with being in
a f-freezing place like this!
It's all D-Dhoulmagus's fault!

<voice_0x010012D2><se_low>King Trode: Oh, but he's d-dead now. So I suppose it's that L-Leo-what's-his-name's fault. I don't know!
A d-dog of all things!
<voice_0x010012D4><se_low>Yangus: Oh, stop yer whingin', Grandad! It ain't as if we've got a sweat on, y'know! Just get on wiv it!
<voice_0x010012D5><se_high>Jessica: Oh, please! Give it a rest! Complaining the whole time won't make it any warmer, you know!

<voice_0x010012D6><se_def>Angelo: For goodness' sake!
You're not the only one who's cold, you know!

<voice_0x010012DC><se_low>King Trode: I beg your pardon! How uncalled for!
I don't see why I shouldn't be able to say whatever I p-please!

<voice_0x010012DD><se_low>King Trode: You've no right to talk to me like that!
No right at all!

<voice_0x010012DE><se_low>King Trode: I'm absolutely livid! Livid, I tell you!
I'm going on ahead!
<voice_0x010012DF><se_low>King Trode: Why are you looking at me like that!? Spit it out! Have you got some kind of problem with me, boy!?
<voice_0x010012E0><se_low>King Trode: Is that all you've got to say for yourself!? Well! Your silence speaks volumes!
<voice_0x010012E1><se_low>King Trode: I don't know, just looking at you at the moment makes my blood boil! I'm going on ahead!

<voice_0x010012DB><se_low>Morrie: Si, Don Toad, I understand your feelings.
But we are all in the same boats here.
Keep your chattering teeth to yourself, ay?
